# pH7Console - Git Attributes Configuration

# === Text Files ===
* text=auto eol=lf

# === Source Code ===
*.rs text diff=rust
*.toml text
*.ts text
*.tsx text
*.js text
*.jsx text
*.json text
*.md text
*.yml text
*.yaml text

# === Configuration Files ===
*.conf text
*.config text
*.ini text
